self.test_plugin.get_shared_messages(None).should.equal(None)
json_string = json.dumps({'shared_messages': {'message_name': ['id1', 'id2',
    'id3'], 'message_name2': 'id4'}})
json_string = shlex.quote(json_string)
self.test_plugin.get_shared_messages(json_string).should.equal({
    'message_name': ['id1', 'id2', 'id3'], 'message_name2': 'id4'})
json_string = json.dumps({'shared_messages': {'message_name': 4,
    'message_name2': 'id4'}})
json_string = shlex.quote(json_string)
self.test_plugin.get_shared_messages(None).should.equal(None)
json_string = json.dumps({'wrong key': {'message_name': 4, 'message_name2':
    'id4'}})
json_string = shlex.quote(json_string)
self.test_plugin.get_shared_messages(None).should.equal(None)
json_string = json.dumps({'wrong key': {'5': 'id2', 'message_name2': 'id4'}})
json_string = shlex.quote(json_string)
self.test_plugin.get_shared_messages(None).should.equal(None)
